<U+2022> [[Louis Nicolas Davout]] (March 22, 1809)<br/>
'''II Class''' (10 awarded):<br/>
<U+2022> [[J<U+00F3>zef Zaj<U+0105>czek]] (February 1, 1808)<br/>
